Research methods
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Both of our approaches share important limitations with the earlier work
 in this area, particularly with regard to questions of causality and potential
 omitted variables.
 Nevertheless, we believe that each contributes significant methodological
 advances on the previous state of the art.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Our survey-based research on retrospective happiness evaluations (chapters
 
