\begin_layout Standard
As noted above, we are particularly optimistic regarding the prospects for
 future research using the spatial experience sampling technique.
 As a powerful new method, it offers plenty of low-hanging fruit.
 Below, we list ideas for potential extensions.
 Time constraints --- partly imposed by the unavailability of the necessary
 consumer technology at the start of the research process --- prevented
 these points from being addressed within this thesis.
 
\end_layout

